			<h2 class="subject">Library News</h2>
</div>
		    </div>
		</div>    
	<div class="art-BlockContent content">
	    <div class="art-BlockContent-body">
	
		<p><strong>Hours for ECRL Headquarters will return to 9am - 5pm&nbsp;beginning Tuesday, Septmeber 6, 2016</strong></p>
<p>Questions? Concerns? If so contact Chief Librarian, Laura Emery at lemery@nsme.library.ns.ca&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #008080">Introducing Zinio! Digital magazines are now available at your library. </span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0,128,128)">Click &quot;Zinio for libraries&quot;&nbsp;icon below to try it out.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000080"><a href="https://www.rbdigital.com/novascotialibraries/service/zinio" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/sites/default/files/images/Zinio_4Lib_horz.png" style="height: 46px; width: 160px" /></a></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000"><a href="https://vimeo.com/107853239">Zinio&nbsp;video tutorial</a></span></p>
<p>Get in the mood for Spring by researching your family tree! Don&#39;t forget that the Library now has access to Ancestry (In-Library use only).&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://ancestrylibrary.com"><img alt="" src="/sites/default/files/images/ancestry.jpg" style="height: 34px; width: 147px; float: left" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
