		    <div>
		        <div class="t">	
			<h2 class="subject">3D printing @ the Library</h2>
</div>
		    </div>
		</div>    
	<div class="art-BlockContent content">
	    <div class="art-BlockContent-body">
	
		<p><a href="http://youtu.be/9KiHKSt77-o"><img alt="" src="/sites/default/files/images/photo-2.JPG" style="width: 150px; height: 112px;" /></a></p>
<p>Click the image and check out our new 3D printing video!</p>
<p>The Library now offers 3D printing services. Printing costs $1 per hour of printing time. Color choices vary.</p>
<p>Visit either the Port Hawkesbury or Petit de Grat Libraries to arrange printing your design. Or email your design to</p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size:12px;">3dprint@nsme.library.ns.ca&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p>We will ship 3D projects to any ECRL location for pick-up.</p>

