  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content">Help Us Decorate Our New Vehicle!</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-body">
                <div class="field-content"><p><img alt="" src="/sites/default/files/images/website photo.jpeg" style="width: 440px; height: 330px;" /></p>
<p>Great news everyone we managed to save enough money to buy a new vehicle for our Mobile Rural Service and book deliveries! We can keep bringing books to your community. We&#39;re looking for ideas of how we might decal and decorate the new vehicle so it attracts your attention. If you would like to make a suggestion send your thoughts to <a href="mailto:lemery@nsme.library.ns.ca">lemery@nsme.library.ns.ca</a> or post your thoughts on our Facebook page.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p></div>
  </div>
  
