  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content">How Libraries Support Health and Well-Being</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-body">
                <div class="field-content"><p>Learn about how public libraries support health and well-being. Read &quot;<a href="/sites/default/files/files/prescribe%20the%20library.pdf">Prescribe the Library</a>&quot; an article published in the Doctors NS magazine this October to celebrate Canadian Library Month.&nbsp;</p></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-addthis-toolbox">
                <span class="field-content"><div class='addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style ' addthis:url='http://ecrl.library.ns.ca/home/how-libraries-support-health-and-well-being' addthis:title='How Libraries Support Health and Well-Being' ><a class='addthis_toolbox_item addthis_button_facebook_like' fb:like:layout="button_count"&gt;></a><a class='addthis_toolbox_item addthis_button_tweet' ></a><a class='addthis_toolbox_item addthis_button_google_plusone'></a><a class='addthis_toolbox_item addthis_button_email'></a></div></span>
