  <div class="views-row views-row-3 views-row-odd views-row-last">
      
  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content">Breast Cancer Resource Collection</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-body">
                <div class="field-content"><p><span style="font-size: 14px">Through a partnership between Nova Scotia Provincial Library, Breast Cancer Action Nova Scotia, and the Canadian Breast Cancer Foundation, new resource materials for those diagnosed with breast cancer and their families&nbsp;are available at ECRL. <a href="http://ibistro.library.ns.ca/uhtbin/cgisirsi/x/0MASTER/0/57/5?library=E_E&amp;searchdata1=10CBCFAR{590}&amp;sort_by=TI&amp;user_id=ECHEWEB&amp;password=pooka666" target="_blank">Check out&nbsp;the Breast Cancer Resource Collection</a>.</span></p>
<p class="rtecenter"><a href="http://ibistro.library.ns.ca/uhtbin/cgisirsi/x/0MASTER/0/57/5?library=E_E&amp;searchdata1=10CBCFAR{590}&amp;sort_by=TI&amp;user_id=ECHEWEB&amp;password=pooka666" target="_blank"><span style="font-size: 16px"><img alt="" src="/sites/default/files/images/BCF_TextQuestionMark_05.png" style="width: 150px; height: 150px" /></span></a></p></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-addthis-toolbox">
                <span class="field-content"><div class='addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style ' addthis:url='http://ecrl.library.ns.ca/home/breast-cancer-resource-collection' addthis:title='Breast Cancer Resource Collection' ><a class='addthis_toolbox_item addthis_button_facebook_like' fb:like:layout="button_count"&gt;></a><a class='addthis_toolbox_item addthis_button_tweet' ></a><a class='addthis_toolbox_item addthis_button_google_plusone'></a><a class='addthis_toolbox_item addthis_button_email'></a></div></span>
